edu.salleurl.profile

Class ProfileFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.salleurl.profile.ProfileFactory

  • public class ProfileFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory class for generating instances of the Profile class. Profiles can be used to generate HTML files representing a Profileable, with some extra information.

    In particular, it provides static methods that return new instances based on the provided parameters.

    Version:
    1.0
